Module it.polimi.ingsw.am01
Package it.polimi.ingsw.am01.client

Class View

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am01.client.View
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventEmitter<ViewEvent>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseTuiView, GUIView
public abstract class View extends Object implements EventEmitter<ViewEvent>
The common view for both graphical user interface and textual user interface. It keeps a reduced and local copy of model data.

It is the client-side point to manage communication with the server:

  • It handles the network messages received from the server and captured by the ConnectionWrapper class
  • It sends network messages to the server, based on the interaction of the user with the GUI or the TUI
See Also:

    • connect

      public void connect(View.ConnectionType connectionType, String hostname, int port)
      It calls the ClientTCPConnection.connect(InetAddress, int) or ClientRMIConnection.connect(ExecutorService, String, int) method according to the specified View.ConnectionType.

      It also instantiates a new ConnectionWrapper to receive the network message from the server

      Parameters:
      connectionType - The View.ConnectionType selected by the player. It can be either View.ConnectionType.TCP or View.ConnectionType.RMI
      hostname - The ip address of the server
      port - The port of the server according to the selected View.ConnectionType
